| [[Erlitou]] || central China (Shanxi and Henan) || ca 1900–1500 BCE 
|-
| [[Monte Albán]] || Oaxaca valley, southern Mexico || ca 300 BCE–200 CE
|-
| [[Teotihuacan]] || Basin of Mexico, central Mexico || ca 100–1 BCE
